OL,3,CJohn Lewis Partnership to hire 13,700
OL,4,CChristmas staff in major recruitment
OL,5,Cdrive
OL,7,FThe John Lewis Partnership (JLP) is
OL,8,Fhiring for 13,700 Christmas roles in
OL,9,Fits biggest ever recruitment drive as
OL,10,Fit prepares for the busy shopping
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FThe retail group, which incorporates
OL,14,FJohn Lewis department stores and the
OL,15,FWaitrose chain, said it was investing
OL,16,Fto meet the expected surge in demand
OL,17,Ffrom consumers.
