OL,7,FThe seasonal roles will include 3,000
OL,8,Facross 35 John Lewis stores, 8,500
OL,9,Fwithin Waitrose shops and nearly 2,200
OL,10,Facross its warehouses and supply chain
OL,11,Fnetwork.
OL,13,FEvery year, JLP recruits for temporary
OL,14,Fshop workers and logistics staff for
OL,15,Fthe so-called "golden quarter" ` the
OL,16,Ffinal three months of the year ` and
OL,17,FJanuary sales period.
