OL,7,FThe British retailer said it was
OL,8,Fexpecting some 30 million visitors to
OL,9,FJohn Lewis shops during that time,
OL,10,Fwhile its warehouses are set to
OL,11,Fdispatch more than two deliveries each
OL,12,Fsecond.
OL,14,FJo Rackham, JLP's chief people
OL,15,Fofficer, said: "We've invested heavily
OL,16,Fto set ourselves up for a great golden
OL,17,Fquarter, but our excellent service
OL,18,Falso relies on having brilliant
OL,19,Fpartners on hand, whenever and
OL,20,Fwherever our customers need them.
