OL,7,F"Whether helping our customers find
OL,8,Fthe perfect gift for a loved one, or
OL,9,Fthe show-stopper for their Christmas
OL,10,Flunch, our seasonal teams play a huge
OL,11,Frole in spreading the festive magic.
OL,13,F"They're rewarding roles, at one of
OL,14,Fthe most exciting times of year to
OL,15,Fwork in retail."
OL,17,FJLP's roughly 70,000 workers are known
OL,18,Fas "partners" due to its employee-
OL,19,Fowned stricture, whereby they share in
OL,20,Fthe profits of the business and can
OL,21,Fhave a say in how it is run.
